/**
 * Shared label set for /kundali (root page + Client + compare + HowTo schema).
 *
 * Authored locales: en, hi.
 * Gemini-translated overlay (sa + mai/mr/ta/te/kn/gu/bn) lives in
 * `src/lib/constants/kundali-page-labels-overlay.json`, generated by
 * `scripts/translate-kundali-page-via-gemini.py`.
 *
 * `sa` is no longer indexed (HTTP 410) but legacy crawlers may hit it,
 * so we still serve translated text there.
 *
 * Article paragraphs that wrap inline <strong>/<em>/<Link> markup are
 * decomposed into label fragments (heading + label/text pairs) so the
 * JSX structure stays intact and Gemini only translates plain text.
 *
 * Resolution order:
 *   1. AUTHORED[locale]?.[key]
 *   2. OVERLAY[locale]?.[key]
 *   3. AUTHORED.hi[key]
 *   4. AUTHORED.en[key]
 */
